/**
 * This is the D3 logo taken right from their website.
 */
var D3Logo = () => (
  <svg width={96} height={96}>
    <clipPath id="clip">
      <path d="M0,0h7.75a45.5,45.5 0 1 1 0,91h-7.75v-20h7.75a25.5,25.5 0 1 0 0,-51h-7.75zm36.2510,0h32a27.75,27.75 0 0 1 21.331,45.5a27.75,27.75 0 0 1 -21.331,45.5h-32a53.6895,53.6895 0 0 0 18.7464,-20h13.2526a7.75,7.75 0 1 0 0,-15.5h-7.75a53.6895,53.6895 0 0 0 0,-20h7.75a7.75,7.75 0 1 0 0,-15.5h-13.2526a53.6895,53.6895 0 0 0 -18.7464,-20z" />
    </clipPath>
    <linearGradient
      id="gradient-1"
      gradientUnits="userSpaceOnUse"
      x1={7}
      y1={64}
      x2={50}
      y2={107}
    >
      <stop offset="0" stopColor="#f9a03c" />
      <stop offset="1" stopColor="#f7974e" />
    </linearGradient>
    <linearGradient
      id="gradient-2"
      gradientUnits="userSpaceOnUse"
      x1="2"
      y1="-2"
      x2="87"
      y2="84"
    >
      <stop offset="0" stopColor="#f26d58" />
      <stop offset="1" stopColor="#f9a03c" />
    </linearGradient>
    <linearGradient
      id="gradient-3"
      gradientUnits="userSpaceOnUse"
      x1={45}
      y1={-10}
      x2={108}
      y2={53}
    >
      <stop offset="0" stopColor="#b84e51" />
      <stop offset="1" stopColor="#f68e48" />
    </linearGradient>
    <g clipPath="url(#clip)">
      <path d="M-100,-102m-27,0v300h300z" fill="url(#gradient-1)" />
      <path d="M-100,-102m27,0h300v300z" fill="url(#gradient-3)" />
      <path
        d="M-100,-102l300,300"
        fill="none"
        stroke="url(#gradient-2)"
        strokeWidth={40}
      />
    </g>
  </svg>
);

/**
 *  Here's some reusable text for our slide.
 */
var SlideText = (props) => (
  <text
    textAnchor="middle"
    alignmentBaseline="central"
    fill="white"
    fontFamily="Poppins"
    {...props}
  >
    {props.children}
  </text>
)

/**
 * This is the whole kit and caboodle!
 */
var Slide = () => (
  <svg viewBox="0 0 240 240" className="wrapper">
    <rect x={0} y={0} width="100%" height="100%" fill="#3274B7" />
    <SlideText x="43%" y="40%" fontSize={18}>Introduction to</SlideText>
    <svg viewBox="0 0 1200 1200" x="72%" y="36.5%">
      <D3Logo />
    </svg>
    <SlideText x="50%" y="48%" fontSize={18}>and SVG</SlideText>
    <g transform="translate(0, 224)">
      <rect width="100%" height={16} fill="white" />
      <image href="../images/pandera-labs.png" x="75%" y={0} width={60} />
    </g>
  </svg>
);

/**
 * This method is required to render the React component, there's
 * some mojo going on behind the scenes.
 */
render(<Slide />);
